  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nAt most locations in the code, inheritance is done without redunancy, e.g.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-contracts/blob/ee149877212acf5564921244b3cdaa7266a372fe/contracts/token/ERC777/ERC777.sol#L29\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-contracts/blob/ee149877212acf5564921244b3cdaa7266a372fe/contracts/token/ERC777/presets/ERC777PresetFixedSupply.sol#L15\r\n\r\nHowever, there are locations where there is an inheritance redunancy, e.g.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-contracts/blob/ee149877212acf5564921244b3cdaa7266a372fe/contracts/token/ERC20/ERC20.sol#L35\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-contracts/blob/ee149877212acf5564921244b3cdaa7266a372fe/contracts/token/ERC20/extensions/ERC20Burnable.sol#L14\r\n\r\n### Recommendation\r\nWe recommend not having any redunancy in inheritances. This makes the codebase easier to understand and read.",
